when the late <strong>Virgil Abloh</strong> was still designing it, but it=
=E2=80=99s nice to see that Bluestar wants to give it a go. I=E2=80=99ve he=
ard they=E2=80=99re making a big investment in the brand on top of what the=
y paid for it=E2=80=94a hopeful signal for those who fear Abloh=E2=80=99s l=
